                            <comment id="14522572" author="hcorg" created="Fri, 1 May 2015 00:53:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please do not close resolved(fixed) issues - they&apos;re closed as part of release process (as far as I remember)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
